"{\n  \"text\": \"I've tried to like beets my whole life and I don't. Raw beets taste too earthy for me. There's just too much of the ground flavor in there. It's a root, but boy does it taste like it, but they're so good for you. That is a truly super fruit food. But I like fermented beets. You lose those earthy tones and it just gets sour. There's a ton of natural sugars in beets. And that contributes to a deep ferment because that's what the bacteria are eating, the natural sugars. These are delicious. I just snap on them. Deep, sour, delicious. Try fermented beets. These are my brand, Scottysfoods.com is where you can get them, as well as all my other uh skim cheese, sauerkraut, vegetables, everything else. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" I've tried to like beets my whole life and I don't.\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 3.76,\n      \"duration\": 3.44,\n      \"confidence\": 0.991,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" I\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.995\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"'\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.922\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ve\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" tr\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ied\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" to\",\n          \"start\": 1.12,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n         